{"tid":773322,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲唔要輕小說可以讓比我","createTime":"2018-08-09T12:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T06:57:12.000Z","uid":176045,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7b7a2dd675b7f446dd1a21ac8c5fe4e7e798a2f0","tid":773322,"uid":176045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:07:46.000Z","msg":"利申左先 屋企冇乜錢買輕小說<br />\n唔係話窮到穿窿 但就算有多餘錢都唔係去買輕小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我黎緊想睇輕小說放鬆下 買本輕小說幾十蚊好似唔太貴 <br />\n但屋企唔太多錢 幾十蚊食到一個星期了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以睇下有冇巴絲有輕小說讓出黎 <br />\n送比我就當然最好 但如果係平平地放比我我都唔介意嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望各位巴絲幫幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果有野想交換可以問下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祝各位新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年願望除左香港建國 共匪倒台之外 <br />\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有幾本輕小說睇下 等自己生活冇咁頹廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299630d3b15c9de2a29186c514ccb66d5f6edfdd","tid":773322,"uid":176045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2220a1949b33bdbe40e791e1d1ab1550a075549a","tid":773322,"uid":94167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"短鳩"},{"pid":"28e7a305954efd97e653b55a448772795d060e42","tid":773322,"uid":60410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T12:58:10.000Z","msg":"夏娜要唔要<br />\nTG: onecut"},{"pid":"05464a6b899052d8f00b7d32f8fdc09c885ca599","tid":773322,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:00:51.000Z","msg":"涼宮春日要唔要"}